# This ChangeLog is maintained by D.V. Wiebe.  Please forward all defile
# patches and other updates to <dwiebe@physics.utoronto.ca>

2004-09-20:
  * decomd.c: Migrate to blog unified output scheme.

2004-09-18 (1.0.7):
  * decomd.c: Print only filename (not full path) to port 11411; report size of
  correct filesystem
  * decomd.c, decomd.8, decomctl: Add versioning

2004-09-15 (1.0.6):
  * decomctl: Typo

2004-09-12 (1.0.5):
  * decomctl: Add control
  * decomd: Move stuff to /mnt/decom

2004-09-09 (1.0.4):
  * framefile.c: Pause state, write to /mnt/decom
  * decomd.1: Add man page
  * decomd.c: Signal handling, better handling of socket numbering, pause
  state

2004-09-08:
  * decomd: Add explicit license

2004-09-07 (1.0.3):
  * decomd.c: Diskspace Check
  * decomd: Verbosity

2004-09-04 (1.0.2):
  * decomd.c, framefile.c: Rename data files

2004-09-03 (1.0.1):
  * decomd.c: Change filename suffix to make defiling less annoying
  * decomd: Add decom channels; add crc and polarity checks
  * crc.h: Add crc seed

2004-09-01 (1.0.0):
  * decomd.c: Basic decom -> framefile pipe seems to work -- need to check it
  with defile, though

2004-08-14:
  * framefile.c: Fox for compilation with decomd

2004-07-20:
  * framefile.c: Remove slow_data stuff from decomd build

2004-07-19:
  * decomd: release
